           ADD  1 TO WS-CUENTA-PAGINA. 
           MOVE CLIS-TIP-DOC TO WS-SUC-TIT. 
 
           WRITE REG-SALIDA FROM WS-TITULO AFTER PAGE 
           PERFORM 6500-IMPRIMIR-SUBTITULOS-I 
              THRU 6500-IMPRIMIR-SUBTITULOS-F 
 
