       2110-CORTE-IMPRIME-I. 

           WRITE REG-SALIDA FROM WS-LINE       AFTER 1 
           WRITE REG-SALIDA FROM WS-CORTE-IMP  AFTER 1 
           WRITE REG-SALIDA FROM WS-SEPARATE   AFTER 1 
           WRITE REG-SALIDA FROM WS-SEPARATE   AFTER 1.

       2110-CORTE-IMPRIME-F. 

